{"tid":2491003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"打了88萬劑AZ疫苗　1死2傷　韓國公眾失信任　韓國政府停打","createTime":"2021-04-16T04:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T07:08:23.000Z","uid":261647,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb20ff7e23b1ec7c8b61109f62e3c3c848543b8","tid":2491003,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:14:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/opinion.udn/posts/5302243053182631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fopinion.udn%2Fposts%2F5302243053182631&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=100444d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/opinion.udn/posts/5302243053182631</a><br />\n<br />\n同為亞洲人種的韓國，目前施打88萬劑AZ疫苗，出現3例血栓，分別是20多歲女性診斷肺部與腿部血栓，20多歲年輕男性診斷腦部CVST但已康復，60歲女性看護死亡後驗出血栓。在疑慮下，韓國已經全面停止60歲以下人群使用AZ疫苗，也暫停本周的學校教師接種計畫。公眾對AZ的不信任已經產生，將嚴重影響6月施打1,060萬劑AZ疫苗的計畫。"},{"pid":"fc6f0b104f9e9b54df9d0393e9ecdbdcae7b52b3","tid":2491003,"uid":155095,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:16:59.000Z","msg":"港共：韓國人真心廢，我地打科興無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131e508f15573036fdd72968f096f3744b041cf8","tid":2491003,"uid":20815,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:18:34.000Z","msg":"88萬劑先1死2傷咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他有冇數據？"},{"pid":"cd603ee1acbaacb7392a0b19e0416d8b213d059c","tid":2491003,"uid":135276,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"88萬先死3個都咁多野講, 叫佢睇下香港啦, 仲要得5成有效咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880d33f6399f037489fb17052daff377bfd7e3a4","tid":2491003,"uid":154373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cd603ee1acbaacb7392a0b19e0416d8b213d059c","tid":2491003,"uid":135276,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"88萬先死3個都咁多野講, 叫佢睇下香港啦, 仲要得5成有效咋<img src=\"/assets/